<p class="ayah 9-106" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَءَاخَرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And others</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُرْجَوْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">deferred</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِأَمْرِ ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the Command of Allah -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">whether</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُعَذِّبُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He will punish them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتُوبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He will turn (in mercy)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِمْ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلِيمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) All-Knower,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَكِيمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">All-Wise.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/9:106" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="1341"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>106<span c