<p class="ayah 9-113" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(it) is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلنَّبِىِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the Prophet</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسْتَغْفِرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they ask forgiveness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلْمُشْرِكِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the polytheists,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">even though</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلِى قُرْبَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">near of kin,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنۢ بَعْدِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after</span><