<p class="ayah 9-114" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">was</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱسْتِغْفَارُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) asking of forgiveness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِبْرَٲهِيمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(by) Ibrahim</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِأَبِيهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for his father</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">because</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّوْعِدَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) a promise</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَدَهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he had promised it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِيَّاهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) him.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَبَيَّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it became clear</span></s