<p class="ayah 9-129" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَوَلَّوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they turn away,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَقُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَسْبِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Sufficient for me</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(There is) no</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَـٰهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">god</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Him.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">On Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَوَكَّلْتُ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I put my trust.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is the) Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَرْشِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Throne,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَظِيمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Great."</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/9:129" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="1364"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>129<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
